Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO WOMEN'S ISSUES
COMMITTEE DISCHARGED AND COMMITTED TO RULES

Title: Directs the department of health to create an informational pamphlet concerning intrauterine devices
Summary: Directs the department of health to create an informational pamphlet concerning intrauterine devices; requires such informational pamphlet to be available on the department of health's website; requires practitioners to distribute such informational pamphlet to patients seeking contraceptives.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to directing the department of health to create an informational pamphlet concerning intrauterine devices
